{"tid":2045083,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一年啦 請面對現實","createTime":"2020-05-31T14:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T15:08:51.000Z","uid":273593,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9fd3cd127ac51b1acaf0ee7b01a468a7cb0351","tid":2045083,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">成日都有人話</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">「濫捕」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 都冇人掉水樽，做咩又射催淚彈?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 阿伯行過都冇鬧警察，又打？<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家認清楚個現實 <br />\n而家狗拉人，唔再因為你做咗乜<br />\n純粹係因為你存在。<br />\n<br />\n對於極權，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「人數」就係最大威脅</span></span></strong><br />\n你當刻做咗啲乜嘢，根本就唔重要<br />\n唱歌定係掟汽油彈，都係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論係遊行，和你sing<br />\n唔該大家落得場，就要有心理準備<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搵定一條安全路線走<br />\n唔好諗住企喺度對峙，佢哋就會收隊<br />\n其實佢哋只係喺度吸引你注意<br />\n方便陣間大圍捕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好耐之前<br />\n無頭緒巴有一個帖係講<br />\n同防暴警察正面對峙係最蠢<br />\n我決定再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論:<br />\n唔係做鬼，叫你唔好抵抗<br />\n人數對於狗嚟講，就係一個威脅<br />\n佢哋一定會清走你<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係呢個前題底下<br />\n請大家好好計劃走/留/去邊<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n六月嚟緊<br />\n一定會有唔同嘅活動<br />\n狗唔想你留低條命<br />\n因為咁樣，你冇得繼續浦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋就會贏咗<br />\n<br />\n小心為上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b895bfd79dc2bea8e1e75e061cbf99db8b7cbe61","tid":2045083,"uid":273593,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同防暴警察正面對峙係最撚蠢嘅方法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n比沙田重要，現場一定想知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313421</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"294d093d62ef32b5ef220389015970c9b6a29bb1","tid":2045083,"uid":273593,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"一定會有人話 <br />\n<br />\n咁返屋企瞓覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好對抗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係想純粹提下大家<br />\n狗嘅處事作風唔再係正義<br />\n見到你犯法先拉你<br />\n<br />\n佢哋覺得只要你個樣會抵抗政權<br />\n就已經拉你<br />\n<br />\n對峙 散水 定係反擊<br />\n我唔會支持反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但麻煩大家 <br />\n要畀啲狗更加高智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5828b2d3d220aa8cdf21c684e6035ff7b92034","tid":2045083,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"總之大家面對嘅現實就係<br />\n<br />\n唔好對峙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1692a3495ca4950617f52fa8e390880e1d03f4bf","tid":2045083,"uid":242323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"其實我認同<br />\n當大家係有共識打就對峙無所謂<br />\n唔係嘅話遊擊最啱味"},{"pid":"de489cfde67363f09d559f7ea8d613fcacaf5920","tid":2045083,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"11fcc07f23b44bd5acb679a8da8ad6ee9ca93dd3","tid":2045083,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1692a3495ca4950617f52fa8e390880e1d03f4bf","tid":2045083,"uid":242323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"其實我認同<br />\n當大家係有共識打就對峙無所謂<br />\n唔係嘅話遊擊最啱味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"我記得有一幕喺荃灣大河街嗰個位<br />\n<br />\n兩邊真係想開打<br />\n<br />\n結果班狗係不斷射催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n然後趁你自亂陣腳就向前衝<br />\n<br />\n拉咗好多人<br />\n<br />\n奉勸大家如果佢地系列陣<br />\n拎曬催淚彈槍出嚟<br />\n代表已經預備好正面對戰"},{"pid":"26ef7eb124c778e96a27a42d527c6caa9a1af421","tid":2045083,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:33:40.000Z","msg":"防暴狗九成九時間個心態都係向前衝<br />\n同埋正面對抗<br />\n<br />\n基本上訓練就係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca303880282cbae9e40505ea0d4970be90aed5a","tid":2045083,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c120a0eaf01f800a98c43f244f0cb99b501d6cbf","tid":2045083,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe55ffe810cfdc71e7709df519687db885bfe745","tid":2045083,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"我地需要更多聲音<br />\n更多報導<br />\n多到好似五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n頭炮好緊要<br />\n唔可以有機會比人spin 或抹黑<br />\n<br />\n飛雲黎喇<br />\n美媒Vice News報道香港獨立既聲音！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2042976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2042976</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n民記係個好開始<br />\n收集大數據<br />\nHK Free Press 立場蘋果要支持<br />\n<br />\n更多更多聲音<br />\n屬於香港嘅真正主流民意"},{"pid":"f4d43738c48a38207e00142361abb8cb8d21a039","tid":2045083,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"除非突然出現數以千計的人"},{"pid":"cb7502bff6e88138ba8775c119de93347d4c124b","tid":2045083,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"c7d66adb97e1d39fbf44f49e46794ca212492825","tid":2045083,"uid":20552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"